# {{lb|en|curling}} The last [[stone]] in an [[end]].
# {{lb|en|frisbee}} A frisbee throwing style in which the disc is held upside-down with a [[forehand]] grip and thrown above the head.
# Part of a [[clock]] that strikes upon a [[bell]] to indicate the [[hour]].
# One who, or that which, [[smite]]s or [[shatter]]s.
#: ''St. Augustine was the '''hammer''' of heresies.''
